      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2d8ad6f6-646f-11e1-b5ed-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
